</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="201" pageNumber="480" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="201.[98,1304,2535,3118]" pageId="201" pageNumber="480">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[100,234,2814,2843]" pageId="201" pageNumber="480">Breeding.</emphasis>
Reproductive activity of the Forest Grass Mouse was recorded in early spring (late August). Shedding was recorded in June and October.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
